{"tid":1969994,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"今日開始，請所有同路人停止使用此膠句。","createTime":"2020-04-12T21:20:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-13T08:24:21.000Z","uid":211994,"like":10,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"5f31b6c5631b8b80e5a848f94f9c8f8623965b05","tid":1969994,"uid":211994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T21:20:15.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">乜野叫做「黃藍是政見」？</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n睇開連登可能唔多覺，但出到去其他媒體平台就間唔中都會見到呢句句子。<br />\n本人希望大家唔好再講，原因有二：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">一.不合邏輯</span><br />\n<br />\n當一個人講得出「黑警死全家」、「香港人報仇」，即係佢認為黑警做嘅事<span style=\"color: red;\">泯滅人性、不人道不道德、侵害人權。</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但佢轉個頭又話「黃藍是政見」，咁即係點？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />班狗做埋啲傷天害理嘅事係要落地獄，但支持佢地同佢地背後嘅港共就係觀點與角度嘅問題？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n虛偽，除咗平時同啲唔熟嘅人傾計，用嚟粉飾太平之外，我真係諗唔明點解會咁講。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">藍絲同黑警冇分別，佢地做咗大大小小嘅野去支持班狗，佢地就係狗嘅一分子。</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n眼前笑住同你傾計嘅藍師奶，可能有份派過飯盒比隻狗。<br />\n而個隻狗尋晚拗斷咗位男手足嘅手，然後喺佢面前強姦咗佢女朋友。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">二.營造出黃藍對立嘅局面</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">你班柒頭反對派憑乜野覺得可以同我地對立？</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我地唔係/唔單止係黃，係主流派、係民意、係追求緊高尚嘅價值，<span style=\"color: red;\">我地做嘅事係正確嘅。</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢地唔係藍，係<span style=\"color: red;\">反對派、係少數、係卑鄙無恥下流賤格嘅人種</span>、讀幾多聖賢書都挽救唔到佢地卑劣嘅本性。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n就好似由稱呼TVB，變成CCTVB咁<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">不要說：「佢好似係藍...<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」<br />\n說：「條仆街係反對派嚟㗎！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」<br />\n</span><br />\n支持政府就係原罪，要大大聲咁鬧柒班少數派，令佢地抬唔起頭做人，令佢地以支持港共黑警為恥。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">「唔理淺藍深藍，反對派全撚柒部都要落地獄」</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n請將鬥黃嘅力氣，用喺追擊少數派上面。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n敵人就喺我地眼前，唔好執著個少部分冗員揸流攤。<br />\n提出可行有效嘅方案，同時集中火力去批鬥少數派。<br />\n<br />\n大家有咩意見嘅，歡迎一齊嚟討論。"},{"pid":"b47580ce9cb21429fbd63fb6143a661cc762d6bf","tid":1969994,"uid":211994,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T21:22:16.000Z","msg":"唔知把口最毒嘅連登仔可以諗到咩句子辱罵下班少數派呢？"},{"pid":"da7ea4601e1264f5b95f6164ba581038e76faf49","tid":1969994,"uid":211994,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T21:23:15.000Z","msg":"不要說：「藍絲」，請說：「少數反對派」"},{"pid":"b7b698bd54e9c02ed0e5c4e692bb1f59af021e4c","tid":1969994,"uid":211994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T21:23:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"43bb973f4f15d15c23008512aab361093c8ba776","tid":1969994,"uid":211994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T21:23:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6a3164dcf5cf417cab772926bbce6d2342b3c09e","tid":1969994,"uid":211994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T21:24:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8c112acafae4fed2d1f1d508f5173347aea72005","tid":1969994,"uid":211994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T21:24:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1f882ffb74c7ad91132b493cd0cb271ef6c9983e","tid":1969994,"uid":211994,"like":0,"dislike":